---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: ""
beschreibung: "Politische Kommunikation, Webentwicklung, Videoproduktion und alles dazwischen. Jannis Hutt, Berlin."
eleventyImport:
  collections: ["portfolio"]
---

{# ── Hero ── #}
<section class="hero" aria-label="Einleitung">
  <canvas class="hero-network" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-portrait">
      {% imageLCP "./src/assets/img/portrait.jpg", "Jannis Hutt", "(max-width: 860px) 6rem, 11rem" %}
    </div>
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="label">Jannis Hutt</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        all things <span class="accent">digital</span>.
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Digitale politische Kommunikation von A bis Z.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#kontakt" class="btn btn-primary">Kontakt aufnehmen</a>
        <a href="#ueber-mich" class="btn btn-secondary">Über mich</a>
        <a href="#portfolio" class="btn btn-ghost">Was ich so mache &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── Über mich ── #}
<section class="section" id="ueber-mich" aria-labelledby="h-ueber-mich">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="label">Über mich</p>
    <h2 class="section-title" id="h-ueber-mich">Moin.</h2>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-copy">
        <p>Mein Name ist Jannis und ich lebe und arbeite in Berlin. Seit 2015 treibe ich mich in Parlamenten herum; seit 2017 im Bundestag. Aktuell bin ich Referent für Digitalisierung und digitale politische Kommunikation bei der Fraktion Die Linke im Bundestag.</p>
        <p>Dabei sitze ich schon immer an einer Schnittstelle: Mit meiner Leidenschaft für Politik und Kommunikation auf der einen Seite – und ihren digitalen Distributionswegen auf der anderen. Sei es Kampagnenplanung, Pressearbeit, Grafik- oder Webdesign, Photo- und Videographie oder Aufbau und Administration der darunterliegenden Infrastruktur. Ich kenne den kompletten Weg vom Anfang bis zum Ende.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── Portfolio ── #}
<section class="section" id="portfolio" aria-labelledby="h-portfolio">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="label">Portfolio</p>
    <h2 class="section-title" id="h-portfolio">Was ich so mache</h2>

    <!-- Filter-Zeile 1: Art -->
    {% set alleArten = collections.portfolio | alleWerte("art") %}
    <div class="filter-bar filter-bar--primary" id="filter-art" role="group" aria-label="Nach Art filtern">
      <button class="filter-chip" data-value="" aria-pressed="false">Alle</button>
      {% for art in alleArten %}
        <button class="filter-chip" data-value="{{ art }}" aria-pressed="false">{{ art }}</button>
      {% endfor %}
      <button aria-label="Hervorgehobene Jobs oder Projekte" class="filter-chip" id="filter-featured" aria-pressed="true" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.3em;">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon>
        </svg>
      </button>

    </div>

    {# ── Filter-Zeile 2: Skills ── #}
    {% set alleSkills = collections.portfolio | alleWerte("skills") %}
    <div
      class="filter-bar filter-bar--secondary is-collapsed"
      id="filter-skills"
      role="group"
      aria-label="Nach Skill filtern"
      data-filter-group="skills">
      <button class="filter-chip filter-chip--sm" data-value="" aria-pressed="true">Alle</button>
      {% for skill in alleSkills %}
        <button class="filter-chip filter-chip--sm" data-value="{{ skill }}" aria-pressed="false">{{ skill }}</button>
      {% endfor %}
      <button
        class="filter-expand-btn"
        id="skills-expand-btn"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="filter-skills">
        Mehr ▾
      </button>
    </div>

    {# ── Cards ── #}
    <div class="card-grid-wrap">
      <div class="card-grid" id="portfolio-grid"
        data-limit="{{ site.portfolio.num_items }}"
        data-limit-mobile="{{ site.portfolio.num_items_mobile }}">
        {% for item in collections.portfolio %}
          <div
            class="card"
            data-art="{{ item.data.art }}"
            data-skills="{{ item.data.skills }}"
            data-featured="{{ 'true' if item.data.featured else 'false' }}"
            aria-label="{{ item.data.title }}">

            {# Media #}
            {% if item.data.youtube %}
              <div class="card-media card-media--yt">
                <lite-youtube
                  videoid="{{ item.data.youtube }}"
                  playlabel="Video abspielen: {{ item.data.title }}">
                  {% ytThumb item.data.youtube,
                  item.data.title %}
                  <div class="yt-consent-hint" slot="button">
                    Mit Klick wird eine Verbindung zu YouTube hergestellt.
                  </div>
                </lite-youtube>
              </div>
            {% elif item.data.bild %}
              <div class="card-media">
                <button type="button" class="lightbox-trigger" aria-label="Bild vergrößern: {{ item.data.title }}">
                  {% image "./src/assets/img/" + item.data.bild, item.data.title, "(max-width: 600px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 50vw, 400px" %}
                </button>
              </div>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="card-body">

              {# Art-Badge + Jahr in einer Zeile #}
              <div class="card-meta-top">
                {% set jahr = item.page.fileSlug | jahrAusSlug %}
                {% if jahr %}
                  <span class="card-year">{{ item.data.zeitraum }}</span>
                {% endif %}
                <span class="card-tag">{{ item.data.art }}</span>
              </div>

              <h3 class="card-title">
                {% if item.data.title_url %}
                  <a href="{{ item.data.title_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
                {% else %}
                  {{ item.data.title }}
                {% endif %}
              </h3>

              {% if item.data.rolle %}
                <p class="card-rolle">{{ item.data.rolle }}</p>
              {% endif %}

              <div class="card-copy">{{ item.templateContent | safe }}</div>

              {# Skills als Badges #}
              {% if item.data.skills %}
                <div class="meta-tags">
                  {% for skill in item.data.skills %}
                    <span class="meta-badge">{{ skill }}</span>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              {# Externe Links #}
              {% if item.data.links %}
                <div class="meta-tags">
                  {% for link in item.data.links %}
                    <a href="{{ link.url }}" class="btn btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="font-size:var(--text-xs)">
                      {{ link.titel }} ↗
                    </a>
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              {# Referenzen / Presse – Beschriftung per Markdown steuerbar #}
              {% if item.data.referenzen %}
                <details>
                  <summary class="refs-summary">
                    <span class="refs-arrow" aria-hidden="true">▶</span>
                    {{ item.data.referenzen_label if item.data.referenzen_label else "Referenzen" }}
                    ({{ item.data.referenzen | length }})
                  </summary>
                  <div class="refs-list">
                    {% for ref in item.data.referenzen %}
                      <a href="{{ ref.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ ref.titel }}</a>
                    {% endfor %}
                  </div>
                </details>
              {% endif %}

            </div>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cards-more-btn-wrap">
      <button id="cards-more-btn" class="btn btn-secondary">Mehr</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── Accent Block ── #}
<div class="accent-block">
  <canvas class="accent-network" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div class="accent-block-content">
    <h2>Immer mittendrin.</h2>
    <p>An der Schnittstelle zwischen Technologie, Politik und Gesellschaft.</p>
  </div>
</div>

{# ── Kontakt ── #}
<section class="section" id="kontakt" aria-labelledby="h-kontakt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="label">Kontakt</p>
    <h2 class="section-title" id="h-kontakt">Schreib mir.</h2>
    <p style="max-width:56ch; color:var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom:var(--space-10)">
      Nein, wirklich, schreib mir. Solange es keine wüsten Beschimpfungen
      oder Morddrohungen sind, freue ich mich über jede Nachricht.
    </p>
    <div class="contact-grid">

      <div class="contact-links">
        <div class="contact-link-row">
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.kontakt.email }}" class="contact-link">
            <span class="contact-link-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m2 7 10 7 10-7"/></svg>
            </span>
            {{ site.kontakt.email }}
          </a>
          <a class="contact-link" id="pgp-modal-btn" aria-label="PGP Key Modal öffnen" style="padding-inline: var(--space-4);">
            <span class="contact-link-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
            </span>
            PGP
          </a>
        </div>
        <a href="{{ site.kontakt.signal }}" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="flex: 1;">
          <span class="contact-link-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          </span>
          Signal
        </a>
        <a rel="me" href="{{ site.kontakt.mastodon }}" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener me">
          <span class="contact-link-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M21.327 8.566c0-4.339-2.843-5.61-2.843-5.61-1.433-.658-3.894-.935-6.451-.956h-.063c-2.557.021-5.016.298-6.45.956 0 0-2.843 1.272-2.843 5.61 0 .993-.019 2.181.012 3.441.103 4.243.778 8.425 4.701 9.463 1.809.479 3.362.579 4.612.51 2.268-.126 3.541-.809 3.541-.809l-.075-1.646s-1.621.511-3.441.449c-1.804-.062-3.707-.194-3.999-2.409a4.523 4.523 0 0 1-.04-.621s1.77.433 4.014.536c1.372.063 2.658-.08 3.965-.236 2.506-.299 4.688-1.843 4.962-3.254.434-2.223.398-5.424.398-5.424zm-3.353 5.59h-2.081V9.057c0-1.075-.452-1.62-1.357-1.62-1 0-1.501.647-1.501 1.927v2.791h-2.069V9.364c0-1.28-.501-1.927-1.501-1.927-.905 0-1.357.545-1.357 1.62v5.099H6.026V8.903c0-1.074.273-1.927.823-2.558.566-.631 1.307-.955 2.228-.955 1.065 0 1.872.409 2.405 1.228l.518.869.519-.869c.533-.819 1.34-1.228 2.405-1.228.92 0 1.662.324 2.228.955.549.631.822 1.484.822 2.558v5.253z"/></svg>
          </span>
          @jannis@hutt.social
        </a>
        <a href="{{ site.kontakt.github }}" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="contact-link-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0 1 12 6.844a9.59 9.59 0 0 1 2.504.337c1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.02 10.02 0 0 0 22 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"/></svg>
          </span>
          github.com/hutt
        </a>
      </div>

      {# Kontaktformular #}
      <form
        class="form"
        id="kontakt-form"
        action="/api/kontakt"
        method="POST"
        novalidate
        aria-label="Kontaktformular">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="f-name">Name</label>
            <input
              id="f-name"
              name="name"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Dein Name"
              autocomplete="name"
              required>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="f-email">E-Mail</label>
            <input
              id="f-email"
              name="email"
              type="email"
              placeholder="mail@example.com"
              autocomplete="email"
              required>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="f-betreff">Betreff</label>
          <input
            id="f-betreff"
            name="betreff"
            type="text"
            placeholder="Worum geht es?"
            required>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="f-nachricht">Nachricht</label>
          <textarea
            id="f-nachricht"
            name="nachricht"
            placeholder="Deine Nachricht …"
            required></textarea>
        </div>
        {# Honeypot-Feld gegen Spam #}
        <div style="display:none" aria-hidden="true">
          <input name="website" type="text" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
        </div>
        <div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Nachricht senden</button>
        </div>
        <div class="form-status" id="form-status" role="alert" aria-live="polite"></div>
      </form>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Modal Lightbox -->
<dialog id="lightbox-modal" class="modal lightbox-modal">
  <div class="modal-inner lightbox-inner">
    <button type="button" class="modal-close" aria-label="Schließen" formmethod="dialog">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 6 6 18"/><path d="m6 6 12 12"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="lightbox-content" id="lightbox-content">
      <!-- Bild wird per JS eingefügt -->
    </div>
  </div>
</dialog>

<!-- Modal Dialog -->
<dialog id="pgp-modal" class="modal">
  <div class="modal-inner">
    <button type="button" class="modal-close" aria-label="Schließen" formmethod="dialog">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 6 6 18"/><path d="m6 6 12 12"/></svg>
    </button>
    <h3 class="modal-title">Verschlüsselte E-Mails senden</h3>
    <p class="modal-text">
      Du kannst mir gerne PGP-verschlüsselte E-Mails senden. Für meine E-Mail-Adresse <a href="mailto:{{ site.kontakt.email }}">{{ site.kontakt.email }}</a> gibt es einen PGP-Key mit folgendem Fingerprint:<br>
      <code style="display: block; margin-top: var(--space-2); padding: var(--space-2); background: var(--color-surface-offset); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-text);">{{ site.kontakt.pgp_fingerprint }}</code>
    </p>
    <div class="modal-actions">
      {# <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary modal-close-btn">Fenster schließen</button> #}
      <a href="/pubkey.asc" download class="btn btn-primary">PGP-Key herunterladen</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</dialog>